### [Psalms Chapter 85](../../../bib/kjv/psa085.htm#001.md)

[Psalms](../../../bib/kjv/psa001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">psa 85:0</span></span>

Overview

[Psa 85:1](../../../bib/kjv/psa085.htm#001.md), The Psalmist, out of the
experience of former mercies, prays for the continuance thereof; [Psa
85:8](../../../bib/kjv/psa085.htm#008.md), He promises to wait thereon, out
of confidence of God's goodness.

